Package it.uniroma2.sel.simlab.jeqn.waiting.times

Provides policies related to time aspects.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    QueuesSwitchingTimes
    Defines the interface for the structure containing the switching times between all the queues in a Multi-queue structure.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConstantSwitchingTimes
    Implements the switching times in the changing of the queue (in a multi-queue structure) to be served.
    NullSwitchingTimes
    Implements a matrix of switching times, in which all the times are null
    SwitchingTimesFileCreator  
    UniformSwitchingTimes
    Implements a switching time class, in which all the times are the same
